==Advanced Settings window: Competitors section==
{{en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Advanced Settings}}
The Competitors section allows you to set various options related to the [[en/Development/Script/Main Page]] and [[en/Manual/Multiplayer]]. The purpose of the available settings is explained below. For each setting, the respective variable from the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg|config file]] is listed as well, together with it's possible values.

__TOC__

===Computer players===
====Allow AIs in multiplayer====
Enables computer players in multiplayer games. The number of computer players can be set through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Difficulty|difficulty settings]] window.
<br />([ai] ai_in_multiplayer = <true|false>)

====Disable trains for computer====
Computer cannot build [[en/Manual/Trains]] or [[en/Manual/Railway construction|rail infrastucture]].
<br />([ai] ai_disable_veh_train = <true|false>)

====Disable road vehicles for computer====
Computer cannot build [[en/Manual/Road vehicles]] or [[en/Manual/Roadway construction|roads]].
<br />([ai] ai_disable_veh_roadveh = <true|false>)

====Disable aircraft for computer====
Computer cannot build [[en/Manual/Aircraft]] or [[en/Manual/Airports]].
<br />([ai] ai_disable_veh_aircraft = <true|false>)

====Disable ships for computer====
Computer cannot build [[en/Manual/Ships]].
<br />([ai] ai_disable_veh_ship = <true|false>)

====#opcodes befor AI is suspended====
Lower this value if the AI is making the game run slow. Increase this value if you find the AI doing a lot of nothing instead of actually building stuff. Leave value at 10,000 if unsure.
<br />([ai] ai_max_opcode_till_suspend = <5000-250000>)

===Allow sending money to other companies===
Allows you to donate money to other companies.
<br />([economy] give_money = <true|false>)

===Allow buying shares from other companies===
Allows you to enable or disable the ability to [[en/Manual/Economy|buy shares]] from competitors. You also have to wait for the company to get old enough before buying 25% or a full take over. This age is about 7 years old.
<br />([economy] allow_shares = <true|false>)





